pullRequest.body:
The Carathéodory extension Theorem

---

3rd and final PR on the way to the Carathéodory extension Theorem. Show that the inducedOuterMeasure from an AddConent on a SetSemiring has nice properties. Elements of the sigma-algebra of the SetSemiring are Carathéodory measurable. 

Co-authored-by: Rémy Degenne [remy.degenne@inria.fr](mailto:remy.degenne@inria.fr)

If this PR depends on other PRs, please list them below this comment,
using the following format:
- [x] depends on: #21036

-->

[![Open in Gitpod](https://gitpod.io/button/open-in-gitpod.svg)](https://gitpod.io/from-referrer/)
